text: L100 may refer to: * L 100, a Belgian resistance organisation * Hammond L-100, an electric organ series * JBL L-100, a model of musical loudspeaker * Lockheed L-100 Hercules, the civilian variant of the prolific C-130 military transport aircraft * Mitsubishi L100, a kei truck model * Nikon Coolpix L100, a semi-compact, digital camera * Strv L-100, a prototype light tank design by Landsverk in 1933-34 * Lunar 100 list of the Moon's most interesting regions to observe.
